    "rationale": "The credibility assessment package for COU2 VAD hemolysis prediction has been reviewed and accepted as a complete submission for regulatory dossier inclusion. All 13 credibility factors have been evaluated against the MRL 5 requirements; 7 factors are formally assessed and 6 are documented as epistemic gaps with remediation plans. Project requirements referenced throughout the assessment narrative are traceable to the sponsor requirements specification v2.1. The package is accepted for submission pending resolution of the six epistemic gaps prior to final device submission.",
